OL,3,CSecond World War veteran commemorated
OL,4,Cas saviour of City Hall on 100th
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FCardiff Council has honoured a man who
OL,8,Fsaved City Hall from destruction when
OL,9,Fhe tackled an incendiary bomb dropped
OL,10,Fon its roof during a German air raid
OL,11,Fduring World War II.
OL,13,FIn a daring act of bravery during a
OL,14,FGerman bombing raid on February 2,
OL,15,F1941, 16-year-old Ronald Brignall,
OL,16,Fthen a plumbing student, saved
OL,17,FCardiff's City Hall from destruction.
