OL,7,FScaling a drainpipe with sandbags in
OL,8,Fhand, Mr Brignall extinguished flames
OL,9,Fcaused by an incendiary bomb. Despite
OL,10,Flocal acclaim at the time, his heroism
OL,11,Fwent officially unrecognised
OL,13,FNow, on his 100th birthday, Mr
OL,14,FBrignall has received overdue
OL,15,Frecognition. The Lord Mayor of
OL,16,FCardiff, Cllr Bablin Molik, personally
OL,17,Fpresented him with a special
OL,18,Fcertificate, acknowledging his valour
OL,19,Fand preserving the events of that
OL,20,Fhistoric day.
