OL,7,FHe added: "Dad's a little frail now,
OL,8,Fas you'd expect from someone who is
OL,9,F100, but I know he is thrilled to have
OL,10,Fthis recognition and the certificate
OL,11,Ffrom the council. It's a perfect
OL,12,Fpresent on his birthday."
OL,14,FThe Lord Mayor, Cllr Molik, called Mr
OL,15,FBrignall "remarkable" and said: "I
OL,16,Fknow this is a rather belated honour
OL,17,Fbut it is no less heartfelt and I
OL,18,Fassured Mr Brignall and his family
OL,19,Fthat the whole of Cardiff expresses
OL,20,Fits gratitude for the heroics he
OL,21,Fperformed on that day in 1941."
